  "instructions": [
    "preheat robata grill to medium-high heat.",
    "chop onion and garlic, and sauté in coconut oil until softened.",
    "add ginger and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "thread chicken breast and cook for 5-6 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "remove chicken from grill and set aside.",
    "add fish sauce, sugar, and black pepper to the grill, and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "add coconut milk and bring to a simmer.",
    "add wild garlic leaves and cook until wilted.",
    "serve chicken on a bed of wild garlic leaves, garnished with chopped cilantro.",
    "meanwhile, soak robata-grill wood chips in water for at least 30 minutes before grilling."
